In this project the source code for the MediaTek LinkIt Connect 7681 is
provided in the form of a patch. In order to apply the patch follow
these steps:

1. Download the MediaTek Connect SDK version 1.71.
2. Unzip the SDK and browse to the src/ folder in the unzipped project.
3. Copy the Evothings-MediaTek-Connect-7681-TCP-Led.patch to the path
   and execute the following command:

   patch -p1 < Evothings-MediaTek-Connect-7681-TCP-Led.patch

4. If the patch has been successfully applied you should now be able to
   build the project according to instructions found in the developerÂ´s
   guide.

* http://labs.mediatek.com
